      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="select_course" data-step-uuid="0610a0ac-e0de-401b-b8d9-a1a1c7c873dc">
    <h2 id="select_course" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Select Course</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/643/244/original/555dbfbe-2706-4c7e-a3ec-6a762e25ca51.png" srcset="" alt="Select Course" height="456" width="758">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_B3F00B00-22F5-0135-70FB-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In the <strong>Course</strong> drop-down menu [1], select the course where you want to send a message [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_address_book" data-step-uuid="a932d4ba-e5e5-40e2-80e5-5f41282cf569">
